title: Emergency Action
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: party_affairs
view-if: emergency_act_timer <= 0 and emergency_state = 1
on-arrival: month_actions += 0.5; emergency_act_timer += 3;
card-image: img/sangerbund.jpg
#subtitle: Setting the direction for our newspapers and radio.

Time has come. [+ chancellor +] has taken over the country. We need to act fast and decisive enough before all of the card house collapses. 

- @resource
- @unity
- @weimar
- @rearnament

@resource
subtitle: Two of resources.
title: Resources are must.
on-arrival: resources += 2

Resources are mandatory.

@unity
subtitle: Calm down everyone.
title: Unity is must.
on-arrival: {!
for (var c of Q.factions) {
    Q[c+'_dissent'] -= 5;
}
!}

Unity is mandatory.


@weimar
subtitle: Our political allies...
title: Allies are must.
on-arrival: z_relation += 5; ddp_relation += 7; kpd_relation += 2

Allies are mandatory.


@rearnament
subtitle: Reichsbanner...
title: Rearming is must.
on-arrival: rb_strength += 50; rb_militancy += 0.01

Rearming is mandatory.
